Class AppObj

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Activator, FeedRenderer

    public class AppObj
extends DbEntryHandler
implements Activator, FeedRenderer
    Entry point for application sessions. Typically, an AppObj is created by Musubi, but "owned" by a third-party application. That application can attach application data
